<comment type="function">
<text evidence="4">Thiol-specific peroxidase that catalyzes the reduction of hydrogen peroxide and organic hydroperoxides to water and alcohols, respectively. Plays a role in cell protection against oxidative stress by detoxifying peroxides and as sensor of hydrogen peroxide-mediated signaling events.</text>
</comment>
<comment type="catalytic activity">
<reaction evidence="4">
<text>[protein]-dithiol + a hydroperoxide = [protein]-disulfide + an alcohol + H2O</text>
